 f_s(r) = \begin{cases} \frac{1}{N}, & \text{if }r = R_\mu \\ 0, & \text{if }r \neq R_\mu \end{cases} 
 \int_\Omega f_s(r) d\mathbf{a} = \int_0^{\pi} \int_0^{2\pi} f_s(r) r^2 Sin(\phi) d\theta d\phi = 1 
